data.title: Pride Live Stonewall Day Concert
data.meta_description: Back to Calendar of Events Pride Live Stonewall Day Concert GET TICKETS Date: June 28, 2024 Time 5:00 pm ~ 8:00 pm Don't miss a night celebrating love, diversity, and resilience featuring Emmy, Grammy and Tony award-winner and two-time Academy Award nominee Cynthia Erivo headlining an all-star lineup of performances with Conchita Wurst, Betty, Lina Bradford, and Loren Allred and hosted by E! News' Justin Sylvester. The free concert commemorates the 55th anniversary of the Stonewall Rebellion and celebrates the grand opening of The Stonewall National Monument Visitor Center.
